List recorded sessions, newest first (SRS FR-5)

Usage: hh list [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --limit <LIMIT>  Maximum number of sessions to print (default 20) [default: 20]
      --json           Emit JSON instead of a table
  -h, --help           Print help

Example:
  hh list
  hh list --limit 50
  hh list --json
